2026-05-15	replace all occurrences of long, long int, 
		signed long int, unsigned long, unsigned long int
		by more generic 64bit integer types throughout
		entire code base (not only libgmp but also libmpfr)

		PLEASE NOTE: 'long' is 32bit in MS Visual C/C++ on
		------------ 64bit system. '__int64' and 'long long'
		are the same 64bit integer type.
		'long long' in gcc/64bit is also 64bit, not 128bit.
		(gcc comes with extra '__int128' for this)
		intmax_t and uintmax_t are '__int64' types on MS
		Windows.

